1
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,920
This is...

2
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,760
What is this place?

3
00:00:35,480 --> 00:00:36,280
Could it be...

4
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,440
I...

5
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:39,920
I've time-traveled.

6
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:44,000
How did I travel to ancient times?

7
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:47,440
So it was you playing tricks.

8
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,680
Where are you going, Ertiao?

9
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:55,280
Sister, please save me!

10
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:57,000
A wicked man wants to kill me!

11
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:58,200
Demon, don't run!

12
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,160
Stop!

13
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,280
What are you doing?

14
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,480
Slaying the monster, of course.

15
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:03,960
Spare my life!

16
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,560
This concerns you not. Move.

17
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,440
Young Master!

18
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,400
Young Master, it's a misunderstanding!

19
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,920
This is my Young Lady.

20
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,400
Young Master?

21
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,080
Huh?

22
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:16,720
This is Transport Commissioner, Lord Li Jing.

23
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:18,280
Young Lady,

24
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,680
when you were one year old, the Master...

25
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,520
arranged your marriage to him. Have you forgotten?

26
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,240
What?

27
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:23,200
With him?

28
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:25,120
Chasing a weak girl in the middle of the night,

29
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,560
bullying the weak...

30
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,200
...what a pervert.

31
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,000
I will let you see clearly what she is.

32
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,000
Illuminate the universe,

33
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,960
boundless divine light!

34
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:33,920
Illuminate the universe,

35
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,920
boundless divine light!

36
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,880
Illuminate the universe,

37
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:36,880
boundless divine light!

38
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,160
Reveal your form!

39
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,200
What are you doing?

40
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,000
There really is a monster!

41
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,720
Human Race...

42
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,520
Do not gloat.

43
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,560
The great army is coming.

44
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,880
Men, women, old, and young of Chentang Pass...

45
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:04,200
none shall be spared.

46
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:09,480
Indeed, a spy from the Sea Clan.

47
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,640
The soul was tampered with; revealing its form meant death.

48
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:19,160
What kind of time-travel script did I get?

49
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,960
Sea Clan...

50
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,960
Great Shang...

51
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,960
Chentang Pass...

52
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,360
And a Li Jing...

53
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,360
Could it be...

54
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,960
I'll pull out the dragon tendon, how about that?

55
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,960
You unfilial son!

56
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,120
Stop, stop, stop, hold on.

57
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,600
I'm engaged to this silly boy...

58
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,080
Am I the future Lady Yin?

59
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,920
Will I give birth to Nezha in the future?

60
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,120
I've traveled to a mythological world...

61
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,280
and I still have to marry and raise kids?

62
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,440
Why don't I just...

63
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,640
cultivate,

64
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:46,040
achieve Ascension,

65
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,840
and become a real little fairy.

66
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,840
Miss Yin,

67
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,560
there is something Li Jing must say.

68
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,080
The Yin clan is a prestigious local family.

69
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,840
You are also a lady of high standing.

70
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,120
You should know propriety and laws.

71
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,240
As it is said, propriety makes us human;

72
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,320
without it, we are beasts.

73
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,800
The sages have said,

74
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,680
propriety is the foundation of humanity,

75
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,520
the root of the nation,

76
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,840
and the basis of our Human Race's standing.

77
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,480
Stop, stop, stop.

78
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,840
This is my courtyard, isn't it?

79
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,560
Yes.

80
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,440
You jumped into a maiden's backyard late at night.

81
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,360
Do you call that propriety?

82
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,840
I came to catch a spy!

83
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,240
Those are all excuses.

84
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,760
If you were capable, you would have caught it earlier.

85
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:23,160
Would you need to trespass on a private home at night?

86
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,480
To put it plainly, you are incompetent.

87
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,120
Fine, fine, fine.

88
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,720
Li Jing has important matters to attend to.

89
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,360
I have no time to bicker.

90
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,880
You're not running away, are you?

91
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,840
Farewell.

92
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,360
Farewell.

93
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,640
With that fighting power?

94
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,040
What kind of person is he?

95
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,440
Your subordinate, Transport Commissioner Li Jing,

96
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,680
has urgent military affairs to report.

97
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,960
Requesting to see the Commanding General.

98
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,800
Come, come, come.

99
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,640
My Lord, the military situation is critical.

100
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,880
The Sea Clan army is assembling.

101
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,720
They will attack Chentang Pass any day now.

102
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:07,640
What a killjoy.

103
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,680
Today we speak only of romance and leisure.

104
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,680
Bottoms up!

105
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,720
My Lord.

106
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,640
Commanding General.

107
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,000
My Lord.

108
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,760
My Lords.

109
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:28,320
Li Jing has a military report.

110
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,280
The Sea Clan army is approaching.

111
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,560
A crisis of survival is imminent.

112
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,640
Yet you still have the heart to live in a drunken dream.

113
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,760
If we do not rally the troops,

114
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,600
light the beacons, and request aid from Zhaoge,

115
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,320
what will become of the people in the city then?

116
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,960
How is that possible?

117
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,480
Chentang Pass is impregnable.

118
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:56,000
The Sea Clan has not invaded for two hundred years.

119
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,680
General Li, manage the grain transport well.

120
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,400
Do not try to steal military glory.

121
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,800
You must be hallucinating from worrying about the nation.

122
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,440
I preside over Chentang.

123
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,480
The border reports only small bands of sea beasts.

124
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,320
Where is this great army?

125
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,760
Do you have proof of your words?

126
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,760
I have a witness who can testify.

127
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,240
Who?

128
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,480
A Sea Clan spy.

129
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,760
Where is this spy now?

130
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,320
That spy is already dead.

131
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,720
And it is dead?

132
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,880
How can its words serve as testimony?

133
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,800
My Lord.

134
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,880
Guards!

135
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,960
General Li is delirious.

136
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,280
Escort him back to his manor.
